comments: Gallinari (OKC) is already in Morris' (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Gallinari (OKC) and Morris (DEN) briefly engage and disengage as the pass is being delivered.
Morris (DEN) makes contact to Gallinari's (OKC) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Adams (OKC) is drawn in the air towards Jokic (DEN) and makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) body and affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs prior to his upward shooting motion.
Gallinari (OKC) is already in Morris' (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Dort (OKC) goes to not through Grant's (DEN) space as Grant is retreating away from the contact.
While setting the screen Adams (OKC) is already in Grant's (DEN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact to Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm, and the contact occurs as Gilgeous-Alexander is starting his upward shooting motion.
Adams (OKC) and Jokic (DEN) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Gallinari (OKC) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm that affects his ability to gather the ball.
Gallinari (OKC) is already in Craig's (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Adams (OKC) is already in Millsap's (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Millsap (DEN) makes a slight brush against Paul's (OKC) arm but does not affect his ability to gather on his driving shot attempt.
Morris (DEN) legally contests Paul's (OKC) shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Jokic (DEN) during rebounding.
Jokic (DEN) is already in Paul's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Paul (OKC) does not make contact to Morris' (DEN) arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Dort (OKC) is already in Craig's (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Millsap (DEN) makes contact with Gallinari's (OKC) arm during his drive that affects his SQBR.
Paul (OKC) places his hand momentarily on Morris' (DEN) hip before correcting.

Millsap (DEN) extends his arms forward into Roberson's (OKC) back and alters his legal guarding position forcing him to make contact with Morris (DEN) affecting his shot attempt.  An offensive foul should have been assessed to Millsap.
Millsap (DEN) turns into Paul's (OKC) path and delivers contact that affects Paul's SQBR.
Daniels (DEN) receives the ball on the perimeter and takes two steps prior to releasing his dribble.
Roberson (OKC) legally contests Daniels' (DEN) shot attempt.
